{"tid":141670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"甄子丹演遊戲改編新片《Sleeping Dogs》 扮香港卧底","createTime":"2017-03-03T06:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T01:51:52.000Z","uid":5195,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"429ad0ed143f9d342c8575cc5760fcbb79c93ac8","tid":141670,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"宇宙最強甄子丹近年成功打入荷李活市場，繼拍攝《俠盜一號：星球大戰外傳》（ Rogue One：A Star Wars Story）、《3X反恐暴族：重火力回歸》（xXx：Return of Xander Cage）等大製作，佢將會拍攝一部由大熱遊戲改編新片《Sleeping Dogs》， 《狂野時速》（The Fast and the Furious）系列監製Neal Moritz將會參與製作。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲嘅背景設定喺香港，玩家會以由甄子丹飾演嘅卧底警察沈偉身份投入遊戲，以搗毀全球最大黑幫集團，電影將會有唔少動作場面可以讓甄子丹大顯身手。"},{"pid":"53bcfe97542d24ab2a3113d4f190f14470b1708f","tid":141670,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/141456_8ad99364a5ff011e7730d747652becf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F141456_8ad99364a5ff011e7730d747652becf2.jpg&h=83ae7e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6215dcc69d3e64d85d32d00dcac6fbaca5a0f5e2","tid":141670,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"當真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想睇"},{"pid":"bb76a74ed0809e073422575d3ae8850977a5fa48","tid":141670,"uid":39632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"Sleeping dog 淨係諗起達哥dom條女落車尾箱 連人帶車衝落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3de9fdf1bea7349f4414c38f785f6b6147b733d","tid":141670,"uid":17042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:20:17.000Z","msg":"Wei Shen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d128118380c4333b6bd08234a2a97d943f1a00","tid":141670,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"